{"article_id":"Sa6wWUZ2Y1vCYqxV","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"House Democrats will hold their first hearing on presidential tax returns Thursday afternoon .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"But even the hearing","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"- a broad look at legislative proposals on presidential and vice presidential tax returns -","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"is a cautious step on something","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Democrats have been salivating over for almost four years .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Democrats have been trying to get their hands on President Donald Trump 's tax returns","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"since he flouted tradition","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"and refused to release them during his presidential campaign .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"When he took office ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Trump continued to keep them private .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Vice President Mike Pence has released his documents .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"Before the 2018 election , now-House Speaker Nancy Pelosi told The San Francisco Chronicle 's editorial board","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"that requesting Trump 's tax returns \" is one of the first things","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"we ' d do","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"- that ' s the easiest thing in the world .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"That ' s nothing . ''","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"since taking back control of the House in January ,","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"Democrats have taken a cautious approach","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"to obtaining the documents .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"Ways and Means Committee Chairman Richard Neal , D-Mass. , is the only member of the chamber","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"who can request the president 's tax returns .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"So far , he has n't done it .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Erin Hatch , a spokeswoman for the committee , said","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"Neal expects","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"when he eventually does make the request ,","depth":14},{"id":28,"text":"it could end up in an unprecedented court battle","depth":14},{"id":29,"text":"and he wants to be prepared .","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"\" Chairman Neal is building a case in the event","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"that the administration decides to disregard federal law , ''","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"Pelosi told reporters Thursday","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"that obtaining Trump 's tax returns was complicated ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"and Democrats needed to approach it cautiously .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"`` It 's not a question","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"of just sending a letter , ''","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"Pelosi said .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"`` I know","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"that there ' s impatience","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"because people want to know...","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"but we have to do it in a very careful way . \" `` Our chairman Rich Neal ,","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"I think ,","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"has been very circumspect .","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"I think","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"leadership is about action ,","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"but it 's also about restraint , ''","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"said Rep. Brian Higgins , D-N.Y. , a member of the committee .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"`` Will it occur ?","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"Absolutely .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"The question is when will it occur","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"to maximize the effectiveness . ''","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"Higgins said","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"Neal has not specified a date to the committee","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"that he would make the request ,","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"`` but without question , both implicitly and implied , there will be a request at some point","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"that he will make","depth":15},{"id":58,"text":"to get those tax returns . ''","depth":15},{"id":59,"text":"`` At some point '' may not be fast enough for some of the caucus ' most progressive members .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"`` I 'd like to know exactly what that timeline looks like ,","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"but I do n't see why we 're not moving it quickly .","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"They need to move that quickly , ''","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"said Washington Rep. Pramila Jayapal , a co-chair of the Congressional Progressive Caucus .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"Jayapal said","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"that her caucus was willing to give a bit of slack","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"because of the partial government shutdown","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"that took up most of the first month","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"after Democrats took power ,","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"but progressives were ready to see some movement .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"Thursday 's tax hearing agenda is not focused on Trump ,","depth":4},{"id":71,"text":"though the president could always come up .","depth":4},{"id":72,"text":"Instead lawmakers plan to explore a provision in H.R . 1 , a bill","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"being pushed by House Democrats","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"that would reform ethics , voting rights and money in politics .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"The bill would also require presidential and vice presidential candidates to release their tax returns .","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"The legislation is likely to move through the House ,","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"but it is not expected to pass the GOP-controlled Senate .","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"If Democrats want Trump 's tax returns","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"they 'll have to use their oversight privilege , a role","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"the party relishes .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"\" The House is a separate and co-equal branch of government .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"We have","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"( a constitutional )","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"responsibility","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"to serve as a check and balance on an out-of-control executive branch , ''","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"House Democratic Caucus Chair Hakeem Jeffries of New York said Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"`` We will not be bullied by the president of the United States . ''","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"Even though it 's their duty to conduct oversight ,","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"Democrats will not abuse their power ,","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"Jeffries said .","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"`` The House is going to proceed with restraint with regular order .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"And that ' s why hearings will take place ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"including the one","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"on exploring taxes","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"related to the president and the vice president","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"before any action is taken , ''","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"he said .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":195,"left":0,"right":194,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":194,"left":166,"right":193,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":102,"right":165,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":1,"right":101,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":99,"right":100,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":99,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":107,"right":164,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":107,"left":106,"right":11,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":106,"left":104,"right":105,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":6,"right":103,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"joi